  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Continuing to Introduce New Technologies in the Libyan University Language Classroom</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project introduces new technology into Libyan University language classrooms to help improve the quality of English language training. It will support teachers in developing strategies to encourage students to use technology to support their individual language learning. Outcomes from the project will be: change perceptions of the role, and increase the use of, technology in the universities&apos; English language classroom; this will lead to Libyan universities producing graduates with higher English levels which will enhance their employability.</narrative>
  </description>
